  "text": "r The transient response of this model is being examined in terms of its internal state variables [CITATION_1] , as preliminary to developing a simplified model that captures the error responses and is more amenable to analytic approaches. Early results suggest that spike rate adaptation is the most significant contributor to the observed error responses.",
